movies.title: A Private War
movies.plot: One of the most celebrated war correspondents of our time, Marie Colvin is an utterly fearless and rebellious spirit, driven to the frontlines of conflicts across the globe to give voice to the voiceless.
movies.awards: Nominated for 2 Golden Globes. Another 1 win & 7 nominations.

movies.title: We Are Marshall
movies.plot: When a plane crash claims the lives of members of the Marshall University football team and some of its fans, the team's new coach and his surviving players try to keep the football program alive.

events.title: Southern Airways Flight 932 crashes, killing 37 members of the Marshall University football team
Marshall's first win after the loss of 37 players, against Xavier University

movies.title: Hotel Mumbai
movies.plot: Mumbai, India, November 26, 2008. While several terrorists spread hatred and death through the city, others attack the Taj Mahal Palace Hotel. Both hotel staff and guests risk their lives, making unthinkable sacrifices to protect themselves and keep everyone safe while help arrives.
